thread.title: Your first trade for Friday, May 25

author: Nia Warfield
title: Your first trade for Friday, May 25
text:
The " Fast Money " traders shared their first moves for the market open.
Tim Seymour was a buyer of Lennar .
Steve Grasso was a buyer of Alibaba .
Karen Finerman was a buyer of Foot Locker .
Dan Nathan was a buyer of Disney .
